Fourth Wind Properties is a privately held commercial and multifamily real estate acquisitions and management firm which owns and operates mobile home parks and apartment buildings within the Tampa Bay area. Since 2001, Fourth Wind Properties has been dedicated towards the establishment of several solely owned companies; which acquire rental income properties and development land within Florida’s west coast with a primary focus on mobile home parks. Each of the Fourth Wind Properties exist within very urban areas and are all centrally located near downtown cores, heavy employment hubs, and beautiful Gulf beaches.
